headline: Dell Is Just Beginning to Tell Its AI Story. Buy the Stock.
summary: Dell Technologies  is becoming a high-growth company—and its stock is extremely cheap.  This is no longer your father’s Dell, which made only PCs.  Its legacy PC business, meanwhile, can stabilize and continue to produce steady cash flows.

headline: Hitachi Vantara Collaborates with Supermicro to Deliver Superior Performance and Scale for Mission-Critical Applications and Enterprise AI
summary: Hitachi Vantara, the data storage, infrastructure and hybrid cloud management subsidiary of Hitachi Ltd. (TSE: 6501), today announced it is working towards a strategic partnership with Supermicro (NASDAQ: SMCI), a total IT solution provider for AI, cloud, storage and 5G/edge.
